im hunting in EPs but my stats are far from beeing maxed, im not a 24/7 player <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />Most of the gear checks come from ppl who are working their way to 65 and at that point id go for evasive AAs and INT/CHA. Especially since Ldon favors us as pullers i rather have 280 CHA instead of 300 more HP because a resisted lull wont cause aggro thanks to CHA and 300 more HP is like 1 Hit from a mob
<br />

<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">when you are pulling alot, i prefer 200 more hp over maxed int and cha anytime. maxxed int doesnt decrease the time you need for regening the mana you spent using FM. if you pull good, you dont have to worry about messing. 
