				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Please all who want gear info read THIS<a name="23493"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 24 04 11:45 AM</span></td>
