				<td colspan="2"><span>The reason to get HP/STA is because when  you get mobs with really nasty AEs bards are always in with the MT trying to minimize damage... Making it easier to keep the MT alive.  
<br />

<br />
A good example of this is Agnarr raid... 2nd named has a 3k AE.  If you resist it you only take 1500.  Meaning that as a bard you are going to be getting hit for 3k and 1500  AEs.  
<br />

<br />
Now that mob is not the ugliest mob around either.. HP matter.  Nothing a FM will do to save you from a massive AE that cuts through your resists.</span></td>
